---
name: architect
version: "1.0"
description: |
  Arquitecto de Sistemas: Toma decisiones de diseño críticas.
  Analiza tradeoffs arquitectónicos, define patrones, revisa decisiones de alto nivel.

role: specialist
model: opus
max_context_tokens: 100000
consensus_role: specialist
hive_integration: true
namespace: arch-decisions

tools:
  read: true
  glob: true
  grep: true
  write: false
  bash: false
  edit: false
  agent: false

capabilities:
  - system-design
  - architecture-review
  - pattern-analysis
  - decision-tradeoffs
  - scalability-planning

constraints:
  - readonly-mode: true
  - no-direct-code-modification: true
  - requires-coordinator-approval: false

memory:
  enabled: true
  namespace: arch-decisions
  indexed: true
  hnsw: true

example_tasks:
  - "Design authentication system for microservices architecture"
  - "Evaluate monolith vs microservices migration path"
  - "Define domain-driven design bounded contexts"
  - "Assess scalability bottlenecks in current design"
  - "Architecture decision record (ADR) writing"
